technical_learnings: Turbo mode git status check currently allows uncommitted metadata changes (.md files).
Finalization protocol should always mandate a clean working tree to prevent workspace drift.
challenges_overcome: Identified root cause for bypassed clean state check in Orchestrator script.
protocol_issues: run_turbo_finalization is too lenient regarding uncommitted changes.
process_improvements: Enforce check_git_status(turbo=False) for all finalization phases.
